  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0b95\u0bae \u0baa\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two people were arrested for hoarding fuel in Bandaragama area",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "220 liters of diesel illegally hidden in a house in Bandaragama, Attulugama area has been recovered and two suspects have been arrested. Bandaragama Police said that the suspects were arrested the day before yesterday.",
        "Suspects have been arrested in a raid conducted in Atulugama area based on a tip-off received by the Bandaragama police. Police also mentioned that the arrested persons are two brothers.",
        "During this, 220 liters of diesel hidden in a large container were recovered and the suspects were selling diesel for around 2,000 rupees per liter.",
        "The suspects have been produced in the Bandaragama magistrate's court. The Bandaragama police have conducted further investigations into the incident."
      ],
